description: For sale: $89,900. Check out this well maintained summer cabin secluded on 40 acres in the heart of the wilderness. Updated and well taken care of, this is the jumping off point for all the area adventures. Septic, well, power, Satellite TV and Frontier internet are currently available. Few out buildings to hold your toys. Buyck has much to offer including surrounded by Superior National Forest and has access to Kjostad Lake, Echo Lake, Myrtle Lake and Vermilion River! Drive a bit farther to Crane Lake or check out Pelican Lake. ATV routes, snowmobile routes, state land to explore, multiple fishing areas, resorts and more! State land to the North of this property

For sale: $395,000. Hand scribed log home tucked back in the woods on 40 acres joining public lands. Wind your way down the private drive to this majestic home. 30 inch logs at the base are part of this quality built home. You can see the craftsmanship, from the custom built kitchen island to the arched doorways and hand picked post and beams in the house. The pond within site of the home attracts the birds and wildlife. The covered porches are a comfortable place to relax with friends and family. The dog yard would be perfect for sled dogs and this area near Togo is known for its sled dog teams. This is a perfect property for the person who likes their privacy and the solitude of the outdoors.

description: For sale: $445,000. Easy One Level Lake Vermilion Living At Waters Edge! Newer Year Round Home, Private Level Lot, East Facing Sunrise Views All The Way Across Prime Niles Bay! Apx 2 acres w/325 ft shoreline. Great central location on lake--5 mi to Wolf Bay Lodge, 20 mi to town. Built 2001, 1322 SF, 3BR (all lake view)/2BTH maint-free sided home w/metal soffit & fascia, huge 40x30 3 stall garage, screened gazebo, firepit at waters edge. Vaulted great rm offers beautiful water view, fireplace front wood stove, glass doors to wrap around lakefront deck. Spacious kitchen w/cooktop & newer stainless frig open to great rm, dining & deck--all lakeside. Lakeside main flr master w/walk in closet, spa bath. Main flr guest BR & full bath. Main flr laundry. Full basement offers open BR, area for another BR or fam rm. In flr heat. Dock. Good internet. Compliant septic.

For sale: $250,000. This is a very well kept, fantastic 3 bedroom, 1 bath cabin on Lake Vermilion. It offers a large deck, great lake views and a very large, (about) 30x40 garage! The cost of the association is well worth it. They cut the grass, supply free internet and insurance for the sheds, shared well and septic with 8 other cabins. There is also a resort close by for the company that wants to come up but you really don't want them to stay with you in your cabin. The cabin is sitting on footings with metal I-beams, so it's built very well. This is one you don't want to miss out on!
